            . I am an officer. I was in Fleet-street about five o'clock in the afternoon, and saw the prisoner snatch the bed-furniture from the door, and put it under his coat. I secured him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I saw it lying in the street, and picked it up.</p>
